---
---
<section id="metodo" class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 bg-brown-dark" itemScope itemType="http://schema.org/HowTo">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="inline-block text-[0.7rem] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-rose-light font-medium mb-3.5">
        Mi metodología
      </span>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl lg:text-[3rem] font-normal text-white leading-[1.2] mb-4" itemProp="name">
        El Método NEURO
      </h2>
      <div class="w-[60px] h-0.5 bg-rose-light rounded-sm my-5 mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-[0.95rem] text-rose-pale leading-[1.75] font-light max-w-[500px]" itemProp="description">
        Una herramienta con base en neurociencia para transformar pensamientos, emociones y vida. Cinco pasos que puedes aplicar cada día.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-5 mt-12" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
      
      <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-white/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-rose/20 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-rose-light" itemProp="step" itemScope itemType="http://schema.org/HowToStep">
        <div class="font-heading text-[3.5rem] font-light text-rose-light leading-none mb-3">N</div>
        <h3 class="text-[0.78rem] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-white font-medium mb-2.5" itemProp="name">Nombrar</h3>
        <p class="text-[0.82rem] text-white/60 leading-[1.6] font-light" itemProp="text">Lo que sientes en voz alta. Reduce la activación de la amígdala un 30–40%.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-white/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-rose/20 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-rose-light" itemProp="step" itemScope itemType="http://schema.org/HowToStep">
        <div class="font-heading text-[3.5rem] font-light text-rose-light leading-none mb-3">E</div>
        <h3 class="text-[0.78rem] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-white font-medium mb-2.5" itemProp="name">Explorar</h3>
        <p class="text-[0.82rem] text-white/60 leading-[1.6] font-light" itemProp="text">Sin juzgar. Con curiosidad. ¿Qué generó esta emoción? ¿Es un patrón?</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-white/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-rose/20 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-rose-light" itemProp="step" itemScope itemType="http://schema.org/HowToStep">
        <div class="font-heading text-[3.5rem] font-light text-rose-light leading-none mb-3">U</div>
        <h3 class="text-[0.78rem] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-white font-medium mb-2.5" itemProp="name">Ubicar</h3>
        <p class="text-[0.82rem] text-white/60 leading-[1.6] font-light" itemProp="text">En tu cuerpo. ¿Dónde lo sientes físicamente? El cuerpo siempre habla primero.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-white/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-rose/20 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-rose-light" itemProp="step" itemScope itemType="http://schema.org/HowToStep">
        <div class="font-heading text-[3.5rem] font-light text-rose-light leading-none mb-3">R</div>
        <h3 class="text-[0.78rem] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-white font-medium mb-2.5" itemProp="name">Responder</h3>
        <p class="text-[0.82rem] text-white/60 leading-[1.6] font-light" itemProp="text">Con consciencia. ¿Qué necesito? ¿Qué elegiría sin modo alarma?</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-white/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-rose/20 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-rose-light" itemProp="step" itemScope itemType="http://schema.org/HowToStep">
        <div class="font-heading text-[3.5rem] font-light text-rose-light leading-none mb-3">O</div>
        <h3 class="text-[0.78rem] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-white font-medium mb-2.5" itemProp="name">Observar</h3>
        <p class="text-[0.82rem] text-white/60 leading-[1.6] font-light" itemProp="text">El resultado. ¿Funcionó? ¿Qué cambiaría la próxima vez?</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
